Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.63,0:00:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.42,0:00:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.58,0:00:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito and his team are up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.75,0:00:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They are inside the BABE chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not working.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,BABE is an important asset of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't let it be breached so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.79,0:00:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a connection, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.08,0:00:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The call function has been locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-How can you contact...\N-Shut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.38,0:01:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I did feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.50,0:01:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Yuito's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-This is bad.\N-What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the enemy will have total control\Nover Yuito's brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.54,0:01:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.50,0:01:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me, Yuito?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.29,0:01:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sever the connection now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.29,0:01:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Move...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.21,0:01:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Move...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.33,0:01:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.92,0:01:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanabi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.29,0:01:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They almost took control of my brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.75,0:01:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The believers were acting strange too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:02:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps this was their plan all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.67,0:02:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would they want to take Yuito's brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane helped me regain consciousness\Nvia brain talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane is in Togetsu as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Togetsu's target is Yuito's and my Red Strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.13,0:02:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Save that for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-We should get out of here.\N-Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.75,0:02:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you do that, I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi and the others were captured.\NThey are locked up somewhere in this facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please use BABE to disable all the locking\Nmechanisms of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. We'll see what we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-Arashi and the others...\N-Kasane...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she come to take Yuito's life again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No. She wouldn't have saved me\Nif that was her intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I found the administration mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've acquired access.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:03:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Luka...\N-Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The control seems fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine if you want to help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But we should get ready to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, after we disable the locks
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"DO YOU WISH TO DISABLE THE LOCKS?"\Nwe'll get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,UNLOCKING COMPLETE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.17,0:03:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫A crime in reality♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫For Heaven's sake♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Accepts any fake♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.71,0:03:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫And disappears piling the eternity in fantasy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Won't take it at all, I get sick♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫A girl looking back♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Casts the miracle into the instant world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:04:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Did you lie♫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Did you lie♫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.83,0:04:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Spit the venom♫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I know why♫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've found a game of ecstasy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Red Criminal gets life♫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've never been in love♫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Don’t know when I started\Ngetting sick of this world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫We will fly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Someday I won't be crying♫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've been sacrificing myself\Nnot to hurt anybody♫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,DESIGN CHILDREN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no surprise they would be spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-Kasane.\N-Arashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:05:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys seem to be doing just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have your locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Escape with Kagero's invisibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay there and wait for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it. She told us to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't want you to wander around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The exit is right ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The exit is closing, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:05:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Break through them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Those clones we saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the design children.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka wasn't the only one?\NEven Kasane is one of the design children?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the only explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemies are coming in from 4 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Our priority is to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Carrying so many at once\Nwas so exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero's invisibility came in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You do know me well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, you should thank me more often.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Troublesome jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We are still in the enemy's territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so paranoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Kyoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let you get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for the sake of correcting\Nthis wrongful universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Togestsu's wish
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is to use your Red Strings\Nto secure the right future!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:08:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't the Kyoka I knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Kyoka! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen this side of Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are her words going through to Kyoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If my guess is right,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka's consciousness has been modified.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What else do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.42,0:08:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not Professor Pope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I am Kyoka Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always liked Kasane\Nand the rest of my team.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why are you attacking us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is Pope?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitoyo Pope was the founder of Togetsu Faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She was also a neurology expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka was one of the design children\Ncreated using Pope's gene.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I have her memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I act based on her intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been protecting Kasane
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and helping her develop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting for the awakening\Nof her Red Strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I did all of those to lure Kasane to Togetsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so I could realize Pope and Togetsu's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.17,0:10:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea about my true identity either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really for the sake of our future?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She is one of the design children\Ncreated for this purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.00,0:10:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But despite the mysteries of our identities,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,there are something that never changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The memories I cherish...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I recall those memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I still think of myself as Kasane Randall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka, don't you feel the same as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You accepted the team and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You were always so kind and gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You guided us all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you cherish the memories we share...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.13,0:11:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what comes to pass,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you are still Kasane Randall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the captain who trained us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's who you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a happy ending?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.25,0:11:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's just acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Shiden. Unlike you,\NI don't disguise my romantic nature
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,with a realist's mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I expect you to suspect me as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Our thoughts aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more curious about\Nwhat you were trying to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to give up working as a spy\Nor return to Togetsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.33,0:12:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm one of the design children.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.58,0:12:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a clone created to complete the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no need for me to think\Nabout anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.88,0:12:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Death is the only punishment for my failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That has been my belief for the longest time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I have my own goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I am in no place to say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I made some unspeakable mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be with all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to protect Kasane and everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is what keeps me going forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never forgotten your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, those aren't lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were a little too nosy sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's Kyoka's personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.83,0:13:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Only the Kyoka I know\Nwould say something so sentimental.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But if that was just an act,\NI'd say it's very convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. If Pope's consciousness\Never comes out again,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cut it off for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You might as well just tell her\Nyou'd kill her if she betrayed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You are even more suspicious
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,than the honest side of Kyoka we just saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That pains me.\NIt was me who saved Kasane after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:14:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, I detected multiple people\Nsome distance away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That should be Yuito's team.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They managed to escape safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hope we can exchange\Nsome useful information.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. Let's regroup with Yuito's team.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka is coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We will be glad if you are part of the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, she did murder your father,\NChairman Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there must be a reason behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps she has her reasons to kill me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole Kasane platoon is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Only because of your help. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.79,0:15:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can say the same.\NHad you not called out to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,BABE would have invaded my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still going to take Yuito's life?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I think we need to talk it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not draw any conclusion just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We should discuss it and come up\Nwith a better solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's talk somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Make yourselves at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?\NIs this Kagero's special hideout?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can put it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,why you tried to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It will be hard for you to believe,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but I hope you hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I wanted to kill you\Nbecause someone asked me for a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That person was you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but from 50 years into the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of our future!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Me from 50 years into the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Your story sounds absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I expected that reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If we didn't experience it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:17:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,we wouldn't believe it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the mysterious scene we saw
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,at the Kunad Highway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, Arashi and the rest of the team\Ntraveled 50 years into the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You time-traveled into the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the Red Strings.\NThus, I have the power to travel through time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, you might have that power too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My Red Strings resonated with your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.71,0:17:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the reason the Kunad Gate\Ncouldn't be closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In 50 years, the Kunad Gate\Nwill consume the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you were killed,\Nthe Kunad Gate would disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the future Yuito told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted me to take your life
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,before the situation became out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:18:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be true...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it, my power\Nwas affecting the Kunad Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But I couldn't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You experienced many symptoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those related to the Kunad Gate as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. My future self wanted me dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems there is no other way to settle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We have other problems to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka is one of Togetsu's design children.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, are you one of them too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw it back in Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Those people had the same face as Kasane's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be the design children.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.29,0:19:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.96,0:19:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Such an interesting story.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was in Togetsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I recalled some memories\Nabout my childhood and my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In the flashback, I was known as\None of the design children.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened just recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.17,0:19:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's about as much as I can tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for bringing up\Nyour unpleasant memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanabi is as gentle as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be concerned. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have other information?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard some bizarre stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It was a story about\Nhow humans came from the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, did you bump your head or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you haven't heard the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that story in person?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When we were looking into\Ndata about Togetsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.25,0:20:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it says the environmental changes\Nmakes Earth inhabitable for humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So they moved to the Moon afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A thousand years later,\Nthe immigrants left the Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and founded a country on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That country is New Himuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I find it hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka, do you know anything\Nabout this information?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As a design child, I have some fragments\Nof Hitoyo Pope's memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are things I can't confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have her entire memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I was taught that was\Nthe true history of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just some made-up stories\Nby the fanatics of Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not the case here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The story is totally true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity did move to the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It is also true that people from the Moon\Nfounded New Himuka on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi, don't give me that look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:21:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That look of yours always gets to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero, I always find you mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.04,0:21:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In the distant memory of Hitoyo Pope,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw his silhouette.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Distant memory? From 2000 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero, just who exactly are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Care to explain what this building is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be Pope's hideout?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad, Arashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.46,0:21:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the ark.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.63,0:21:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, it's a spaceship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A spaceship?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was once on the ark.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.75,0:21:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was one of the immigrants who came to Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.75,0:21:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,from the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:22:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,SUMERAGI TOMB
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.58,0:22:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I will realize the legacy\Nof the Sumeragi family
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.75,0:22:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,with Yuito's power...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.42,0:22:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I will save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I don't need to let fate dictate me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Because I believe that I can rewrite it♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.71,0:22:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'll always be a dreamer now and forever♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Another sunrise shines now and it blacks out♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫What's waiting for us at the world's end♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.83,0:23:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Forever eternal, keep the fire going♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.83,0:23:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Who can shake us♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.21,0:23:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Who can define us♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.63,0:23:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♫It's nothing less than our story♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.58,0:23:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Forever eternal,\Nkeep the fire going in your heart♫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.83,0:24:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,TWO THOUSAND YEARS OF LONGING
